<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<task id="040" project="smart-todo-decoupling-r3">
  <metadata>
    <title>Add "To Dos" subgrid to all eleven parent-entity main forms (consolidated parallel-execution task)</title>
    <phase>Phase 5: Parent-Form Subgrids</phase>
    <status>not-started</status>
    <estimated-effort>6-10 hours (11 sub-deliverables; parallelizable to ~1 hour wall-clock when fanned out)</estimated-effort>
    <dependencies>002, 030, 031, 032</dependencies>
    <blocks>none</blocks>
    <tags>dataverse, solution, ribbon</tags>
    <rigor-hint>STANDARD</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>Form XML edits — eleven independent files, no code logic. STANDARD rigor; parallel-safe across the 11 sub-deliverables.</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>P5-W1</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>true</parallel-safe>
  </metadata>

  <prompt>
    Add a "To Dos" subgrid to the main form of each of the eleven regarding-target entities: Matter, Project, Event, Communication, WorkAssignment, Invoice, Budget, Analysis, Organization, Contact, Document. Each subgrid filters by the corresponding `sprk_regarding*` lookup; default view = Active todos; "All" view available; command bar includes "+ Create To Do" launching the wizard with regarding pre-filled.

    **Execution note**: this task has 11 independent sub-deliverables (one per entity). The task-execute skill should fan out into 11 parallel sub-agents in two waves of 6+5 (per CLAUDE.md "Sub-Agent Write Boundary" + 6-agents-per-wave cap). Each sub-agent edits one form's `FormXml`.
  </prompt>

  <role>Spaarke Dataverse form developer.</role>

  <goal>Eleven parent forms each have a "To Dos" subgrid with correct filter + correct command bar. Solution import clean. Each subgrid row count matches a direct OData query against `sprk_todo` filtered by the corresponding `sprk_regarding*` lookup.</goal>

  <context>
    <background>The subgrid is the primary discovery surface for parent-context todos. Each entity has its own form XML, so the 11 edits are independent and naturally parallel.</background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>solutions/{spaarke-core}/Entities/sprk_matter/FormXml/</file>
      <file>solutions/{spaarke-core}/Entities/sprk_project/FormXml/</file>
      <file>solutions/{spaarke-core}/Entities/sprk_event/FormXml/</file>
      <file>solutions/{spaarke-core}/Entities/sprk_communication/FormXml/</file>
      <file>solutions/{spaarke-core}/Entities/sprk_workassignment/FormXml/</file>
      <file>solutions/{spaarke-core}/Entities/sprk_invoice/FormXml/</file>
      <file>solutions/{spaarke-core}/Entities/sprk_budget/FormXml/</file>
      <file>solutions/{spaarke-core}/Entities/sprk_analysis/FormXml/</file>
      <file>solutions/{spaarke-core}/Entities/sprk_organization/FormXml/</file>
      <file>solutions/{spaarke-core}/Entities/contact/FormXml/</file>
      <file>solutions/{spaarke-core}/Entities/sprk_document/FormXml/</file>
    </relevant-files>
  </context>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="FR-17">Subgrid added to all 11 entity main forms; filtered by corresponding `sprk_regarding*`; default Active view + All view; "+ Create To Do" command launches wizard with regarding pre-filled.</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>.claude/skills/dataverse-deploy/SKILL.md</file>
      <file>.claude/skills/ribbon-edit/SKILL.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Author two `sprk_todo` saved queries: (a) Active Todos for regarding (parameterized by lookup); (b) All Todos for regarding. These views are reused by every subgrid.</step>
    <step order="2">For each of the 11 entities (parallel-safe — fan out to sub-agents in waves of 6+5):
- Edit the main FormXml to add a "To Dos" subgrid section.
- Configure filter: `sprk_todos` filtered by `_sprk_regarding{ENTITY}_value eq parent.recordid`.
- Set default view = Active; expose All view.
- Add command bar entry "+ Create To Do" launching the CreateTodo wizard with regarding pre-filled to the host record.</step>
    <step order="3">Pack solution; import to target environment.</step>
    <step order="4">Smoke test each form: open a parent record with at least one linked `sprk_todo`; verify subgrid renders correct rows; verify "+ Create To Do" launches wizard with regarding pre-filled.</step>
    <step order="5">Update TASK-INDEX.md status to ✅ completed.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="pac">Solution pack/import</tool>
    <tool name="ribbon-edit-skill">Form XML + RibbonXml manipulation</tool>
  </tools>

  <outputs>
    <output type="solution">Eleven entity FormXml files with new "To Dos" subgrid</output>
    <output type="solution">Two new saved queries on `sprk_todo` (Active for regarding, All for regarding)</output>
  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">All 11 parent forms render the "To Dos" subgrid.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Subgrid filter matches a direct OData query (row count parity).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">"+ Create To Do" command launches wizard with regarding pre-filled to the host record.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Solution import clean.</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>

  <notes>
    Use the `ribbon-edit` skill for command-bar additions. The 11 entity edits are file-isolated, so a wave of 6 + wave of 5 parallel sub-agents is safe per the project-pipeline's 6-agents-per-wave cap.
  </notes>

  <execution>
    <skill>.claude/skills/task-execute/SKILL.md</skill>
    <protocol>STANDARD rigor. Sub-agent fan-out at execution time per the prompt instructions. Each sub-agent edits one entity's FormXml.</protocol>
  </execution>
</task>
